description: Kona Ice is a unique family-oriented entertainment vehicle serving tropical shaved ice.Kona Ice’s tropical themed vehicle is beautiful, bright, engaging, and interactive! Our “FlavorWave” allows kids of all ages to make their own combination of our wild and wonderful flavors for their shaved ice!Our flavors are made with an exclusive blend called Performance+! With vitamins B6, B12, Niacin (B3), and with 40% less sugar, it all adds up to hundreds of health benefits. Shaved ice has never been so good for you!You can count on Kona Ice being "Most Popular" at ANY event:• State, County and Local Fairs• Fundraisers• School Events• Sports Tournaments• Corporate Picnics & GatheringsKona Ice is a definite guest pleaser! Wherever you find people gathered for celebrations, and fun, you'll find Kona Ice!
